    Paralysis returns and informs Aracnia of what happened. Megatron and 
Waspinator retreated into the mirky swamps, and the Predacons at the cave 
were under attack, and outnumbered.
    "Mmmm....I could use this to my advantage. We could assimilate the 
groups! Contact Kitkat. Tell her that if she alligns with my fraction, they 
we will help her. Otherwise shes on her own." Aracnia commands, while petting 
Quickstrikes cobra hand.
    Paralysis nods and sends the transmission out.
